channel.title: Java Decompiler
channel.description:
Not sure where else to put this, and I read the section rules, it said nothing about this. Could anyone link me to a good Java decompiler? The current one I have decompiles them file by file, its nice though because I can just open the class file, and it shows me the decompiled version, but i'm looking to decompile multiple files. Any help?
Thanks in advance c:
Also, if you would like me to post the decompiler I currently have, just say so, and I will.
